Name: Magneatal™ Billet
Description:
Magneatal™ is FICSIT's internally developed ferromagnetic Iron-Nickel-Cobalt (Fernico) alloy.

Similar in composition to meteorite iron. Highly energetic magnetic fields can turn it into permanent magnets.Crafted into basic Magneatal™ parts.
